description:
This is a Lego animation depicting the resurrection of Jesus Christ. We celebrate Easter today, commemorating a Sunday 2,000 years ago when Christ rose from the dead. This event is found in The Gospels of Matthew 27:65-66 and 28:1-20, Mark 15:42-47 and 16:1-8, Luke 23:50-56 and 24:1-12, John 19:38-42 and 20:1-10

Hope you enjoyed our Easter Special!
